    The enumeration IloCplex::MultiObjLongInfo lists types of solution information of type long that can be retrieved about the solution of a subproblem solved during multiobjective optimization. This information can be queried for each priority level with method IloCplex.getMultiObjInfo(IloCplex.MultiObjLongInfo,int).

    See the documentation of multiobjective information in the Callable Library (C API) Reference Manual for more information about these values. Also see the CPLEX User's Manual for examples of their use.
